    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust 996.2 Carrera featuring the 3.6L flat-six M96 powerplant paired with a precise 6-speed G96 manual transaxle. This example boasts a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a recently refreshed cooling system utilizing a low-temp thermostat. The chassis remains taut with upgraded Bilstein B6 dampers and factory-spec bushings, ensuring excellent lateral grip and communicative feedback through the hydraulic steering rack. While the exterior shows minor road-rash consistent with regular use, the bore-scoring inspection passed clear, and the limited-slip differential provides superb exit traction. This is a driver-focused machine with sorted internals, ready for the canyons.",
